{
  "texts": [
    "Th selfattention mechanism enables the model to effectively capture long-range relationships.",
    "The transformer model is able to address any point in the input sequence, unlike conventional sequential models like RNNs.",
    "It produces context-aware representations for each input token.",
    "Due to the attention mechanism, transformers provide efficient parallelization during training and inference.",
    "The model becomes more effective and scalable as a result of its parallelization capacity, especially when working with huge datasets."
  ]
}